@host = http://localhost:5261

### Login — copy data.accessToken for Bearer requests below
POST {{host}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@demo.local",
  "password": "Admin@123!"
}

### Profile (Authorization: Bearer <data.accessToken>)
@token = REPLACE_WITH_JWT_FROM_LOGIN
GET {{host}}/api/users/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Products — list (requires JWT)
GET {{host}}/api/products?page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
